&lt;DIV&gt;Aye, Hate, The Hole, POV, alot of places a warrior can solo at level 70, we just got to go back about 5 years to find them. Everything is dependent on gear though, a properly gear'd warrior could solo in WOS effectively, long as he has alot of AA's, a good DPS weapon (2hander is what I seen used) that allows him to kill them fast enough, etc. Similarly, a warrior in less then adequate gear can find himself having a hard time solo'ing anything above green con's.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
